<h2>SA Safelist</h2>

<table>
<tr>
	<th class="horizontal" colspan="2"> Actions </th>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td><%= link_to 'Register New Family', 
	     {:controller => 'register', 
		  :action => 'index'}, 
		  :class => 'textbutton'  %></td>
	<td class="note"> <p>Register a New Family -- person does not have a Red Cross
	ID bracelet or number and is entering the facility</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td><%= link_to 'Check-In Family/Person', 
	     {:controller => '', 
		  :action => ''}, 
		  :class => 'textbutton'  %></td>
	<td class="note"> <p>Check-In Family/Person -- person has an ID and is 
	entering the facility</p> </td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td><%= link_to 'Check-Out Family/Person', 
		 {:controller => '', 
		  :action => ''}, 
		  :class => 'textbutton' %></td>
	<td class="note"> <p>Check-Out Family/Person -- person has an ID and is 
	permanently leaving the facility</p> </td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td><%= link_to 'Issue a Temporary Leave', 
		 {:controller => '', 
		  :action => ''}, 
		  :class => 'textbutton'  %></td>
	<td class="note"> <p>Issue a Temporary Leave -- person has an ID and is 
	leaving the facility but plans to return</p> </td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td><%= link_to 'Record Injury Report', 
	     {:controller => '', 
		  :action => ''}, 
		  :class => 'textbutton'  %></td>
	<td class="note"> <p> Record Injury Report -- add a record of an injury in
	the facility </p> </td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td><%= link_to 'Check-In/Check-Out Volunteer', 
	     {:controller => '', 
		  :action => ''}, 
		  :class => 'textbutton'  %></td>
	<td class="note"> <p> Check-In/Check-Out Volunteer -- Add a volunteer or mark 
	that a volunteer is leaving </p> </td>
</tr>
<tr>
	<th class="horizontal" colspan="2"> Reports </th>
</tr>
<tr>
	<td><%= link_to 'View Citizen Roster', 
	     {:controller => '', 
		  :action => ''}, 
		  :class => 'textbutton'  %></td>
	<td class="note"> <p> View Citizen Roster -- display the currrent list of
	citizens registered in the facility </p> </td>
</tr>
</table>

